  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a complex genetic evaluation involving mosaic TP53 variant and its implications for Li-Fraumeni syndrome diagnosis and management.",
    "The patient had multiple breast tumors all harboring the same TP53 variant, supporting the diagnosis of mosaicism rather than clonal hematopoiesis.",
    "Management decisions were significantly altered by the genetic findings, particularly the avoidance of radiation therapy due to increased cancer risk in Li-Fraumeni syndrome."
